snippet.title: Let's Play Hydra Castle Labyrinth - 01 - Maze
snippet.description:
Let's play a game similar to La-Mulana or Maze of Galious! 
This game is made by Buster, who is awesome! http://hp.vector.co.jp/authors/VA025956/
Get the game from here: http://www.vector.co.jp/download/file/win95/game/fh549490.html (New version 1.03!)
And if you're interested in playing the game yourself without too many spoilers, I recommend watching until I get the bell, do that yourself, and then stop watching and play it on your own!
Translation Patch: http://redd.it/hlwfc
